-- RCS Mediagroup Hires Financial Adviser to Help Evaluate Options for Dada
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-09-07T07:24:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-07/rcs-mediagroup-hires-financial-adviser-to-help-evaluate-options-for-dada.html

          
          
             RCS MediaGroup SpA, the publisher of
Italy’s largest daily newspaper, said it’s evaluating options on
Dada SpA, which it controls with a 50.7 percent stake, according
to a statement distributed by the Italian exchange.  
 The company said the process is at a preliminary stage and
no decision has been taken on a possible delisting of Dada, the
statement said.  
          
          


  


        